column6:
On the condition
SERVICE_PACK_VARIANTE = 00b (= FR 2015)
AND
GLOBAL_FAHRZEUG_TYP == 1h (= PHEV, see request 51_12353 FF. in the section “definitions”)
AND
{
{
LEISTUNGSANZEIGE_RUEKO_BETRIEBSMODUS_WOHNEN_ENABLE == 0b (= display of the operating mode in LIVING switched off)
AND
{
PWF == CHECKING
OR
PWF >= FB_H
}
}
OR
{
LEISTUNGSANZEIGE_RUEKO_BETRIEBSMODUS_WOHNEN_ENABLE == 1b (= display of the operating mode in LIVING switched on)
AND
PWF >= LIVING
}
}
AND
E_DRIVE_STATUS_ENABLE == 1b (= conditions for the display of the operating mode are fulfilled)
the conditions are fulfilled for the display of the operating mode in the state line.

